### 1) Update task name
PATCH {{host}}/Tasks/updateTask/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Task renamed from HTTP test"
}

### 2) Update task description
PATCH {{host}}/Tasks/updateTask/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "description": "Updated description from HTTP test"
}

### 3) Set as completed
PATCH {{host}}/Tasks/updateTask/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": true
}

### 4) Set as uncompleted
PATCH {{host}}/Tasks/updateTask/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": false
}

### Optional verification after updates
GET {{host}}/Tasks/{{taskId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
